  <text>
    <body>
      <div type="inscription"  xml:lang="en" decls="#f_S #c_3 #m_I #t_P">
        <ab>SACRED</ab>
        <ab>To the MEMORY of ROBERT</ab>
        <ab>The eldest SON of. MR. ROBERT BROWN,</ab>
        <ab>of the Sity of London, Merchant.</ab>
        <ab>Who unhappily lost his Life at Tivoli by his</ab>
        <ab>Foot slipping, in coming out of Neptune's Grotto,</ab>
        <ab>on the 6th July 1823.</ab>
        <ab>Aged 21 years.</ab>
        <ab>Reader Beware</ab>
        <ab>By this Fatal Accident</ab>
        <ab>a Virtous and Amiable Youth has been</ab>
        <ab>suddenly snatched away in the bloom of Health</ab>
        <ab>and pride of Life!</ab>
        <ab>His disconsolate Parents are bereaved</ab>
        <ab>of a most excellent Son,</ab>
        <ab>His Brothers, and Sisters have to lament</ab>
        <ab>an attached, and affectionate Brother,</ab>
        <ab>and all his Family and Friends</ab>
        <ab>have sustained an irreparable Loss.</ab>
      </div>
      <div type="inscription"  xml:lang="it" decls="#f_N #c_4 #m_I #t_P">
        <ab>Qui Giace</ab>
        <ab>ROBERTO</ab>
        <ab>Primogenito d. ROBERTO BROWN di Londra,</ab>
        <ab>cominciava appena il quinto Lus[....]di sua vita</ab>
        <ab>quando cadde nelle Acque dell' Aniene</ab>
        <ab>dentro la grotta di Nettuno in Tivoli.</ab>
        <ab>Lui infelicemente Mori</ab>
        <ab>sotto gli occhi del fratello</ab>
        <ab>il Giorno vi Luglio MDCCCXXIII.</ab>
        <ab>Siate attenti o leggitori</ab>
        <ab>Per questo fatale accidente</ab>
        <ab>Un Giovane virtuoso ed amabile</ab>
        <ab>e` stato rapito nel fior degli anni.</ab>
        <ab>I suoi parenti sconsolati</ab>
        <ab>sono privi di un figlio eccelente,</ab>
        <ab>I Fratelli e le Sorelle compiangono</ab>
        <ab>un Fratello carissimo,</ab>
        <ab>e tutta la Famiglia e gli Amici</ab>
        <ab>sono dolenti di questa perdita irreparabile.</ab>
      </div>
    </body>
